text: The Kraken Galaxy is a hypothetical galaxy that is proposed to have collided with the Milky Way around 11 billion years ago, before the Sausage galaxy collided with the milky way. == Related pages == * Sausage Galaxy, a dwarf galaxy that has collided with the Milky Way * M32p, another hypothetical galaxy that was collided into the Andromeda Galaxy billions of years ago.
title: Kraken Galaxy
